STATE

Anna Laura HUCKELBA. No. 156A15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 26, 2015. Edward Eldred, for Huckelba, Anna Laura. Catherine F. Jordan, Assistant Attorney General, J. Douglas Henderson, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

Opinion
